<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>Success Card</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      margin-top: 5rem;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #e9ecef;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .success-card {
      background-color: #dff0d8;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #333;
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .back-btn {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .back-btn button {
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #4a90e2;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      border-radius: 4px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .back-btn button:hover {
      background-color: #366dbf;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="success-card">
      <h1>Query Successfully Registered!</h1>
      <p>Your query has been successfully registered. The token number <strong><%= tokenNumber %></strong> has been sent to your given email.</p>
      <p>Thank you for submitting your query. Our team will get back to you soon.</p>
    </div>

    <form  class="back-btn" action="/user" method="GET">
      <button type="submit">Back</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
